><div class="collapse-header" data-v-10734111><span data-v-10734111>What is PolyBuzz?</span><div class="collapse-btn close" data-v-10734111></div></div><div class="collapse-content" style="display:none;" data-v-10734111><!--[--><div class="doc-answer" data-v-54b5cb0a>PolyBuzz offers Free, Private, and Unrestricted AI character chats with over 20 million characters, enabling you to create your own AI characters, dive into immersive roleplay, and explore endless possibilities. Additionally, PolyBuzz is an AI chatbot application that provides personalized conversations and immersive role-playing experiences.</div><!--]--></div></div><!----></div></div><div class="doc-item" data-v-54b5cb0a><div data-v-54b5cb0a data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-container collapse-close" data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-header" data-v-10734111><span data-v-10734111>Is PolyBuzz free?</span><div class="collapse-btn close" data-v-10734111></div></div><div class="collapse-content" style="display:none;" data-v-10734111><!--[--><div class="doc-answer" data-v-54b5cb0a>PolyBuzz is accessible at no cost, or you can opt for a membership to unlock a more enhanced experience.</div><!--]--></div></div><!----></div></div><div class="doc-item" data-v-54b5cb0a><div data-v-54b5cb0a data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-container collapse-close" data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-header" data-v-10734111><span data-v-10734111>Are PolyBuzz chats private?</span><div class="collapse-btn close" data-v-10734111></div></div><div class="collapse-content" style="display:none;" data-v-10734111><!--[--><div class="doc-answer" data-v-54b5cb0a>Yes, PolyBuzz chats are completely private! Your privacy and security are our highest priorities. Conversations with AI characters on PolyBuzz are confidential and secure, ensuring that neither the creators nor Poly have access to the chat content between users and the AI characters.</div><!--]--></div></div><!----></div></div><div class="doc-item" data-v-54b5cb0a><div data-v-54b5cb0a data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-container collapse-close" data-v-10734111><div class="collapse-header" data-v-10734111><span data-v-10734111>Does PolyBuzz have a NSFW filter?</span><div class="collapse-btn close" data-v-10734111></div></div><div class="collapse-content" style="display:none;" data-v-10734111><!--[--><div class="doc-answer" data-v-54b5cb0a>PolyBuzz strictly prohibit public display of NSFW content. All recommended content undergoes multi-layered AI screening and human moderation to ensure community safety. If you come across any illegal or inappropriate material, we encourage you to report it, and we will take prompt action to address the issue.</div><!--]--></div></div><!----></div></div><!--]--></div></div></div></div><!--]--><span></span><!--]--><div class="container" data-v-1628d1b5 data-v-6b048961><div class="footer" data-v-6b048961><div class="footer-left" data-v-6b048961><div class="footer-left-header" data-v-6b048961><div class="polybuzz-icon" data-v-6b048961></div><!--[--><div class="download-item el-tooltip__trigger el-tooltip__trigger" data-v-edf822c9><span data-v-edf822c9>Download</span></div><!--teleport start--><!--teleport end--><!--]--></div><div class="footer-left-text" data-v-6b048961>PolyBuzz is a Free, Private, and Unlimited AI Chat platform with over 20 million unique Characters, offering personalized conversations and immersive roleplaying experiences. You can also unleash your creativity by creating your own AI Characters, unlocking endless possibilities.</div><div class="footer-left-media" data-v-6b048961><!--[--><a href="https://discord.gg/3nsmjy2NA6" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="footer-left-media-link" src="https://cdn.polyspeak.ai/speakmaster/aae330e9586261f1de58db401a2d5107.webp" data-v-6b048961><div class="el-image common-image common-image-v2 media-item" style="" data-v-6b048961 data-v-a8ef40e3><img src="https://cdn.polyspeak.ai/speakmaster/aae330e9586261f1de58db401a2d5107.webp" class